ZH: 边缘化是一种不公平待遇。
EN: Marginalization is a form of unfair treatment.

ZH: 这个社会正在边缘化某些群体。
EN: This society is marginalizing certain groups.

ZH: 边缘化会导致不平等的机会分配。
EN: Marginalization can lead to unequal distribution of opportunities.

ZH: 很多弱势群体正面临着边缘化的风险。
EN: Many vulnerable groups are at risk of marginalization.

ZH: 边缘化使得少数族裔被边缘于主流社会。
EN: Marginalization marginalizes ethnic minorities from mainstream society.

ZH: 边缘化会削弱某些群体的社会地位。
EN: Marginalization can weaken the social status of certain groups.

ZH: 边缘化是社会不公的一种表现。
EN: Marginalization is a manifestation of social injustice.

ZH: 边缘化引起了人权组织的关注。
EN: Marginalization has caught the attention of human rights organizations.

ZH: 边缘化给个人带来了巨大的心理压力。
EN: Marginalization brings immense psychological pressure to individuals.

ZH: 边缘化是社会多样性的威胁。
EN: Marginalization is a threat to social diversity.

ZH: 学校应该努力避免边缘化学生。
EN: Schools should strive to avoid marginalizing students.

ZH: 边缘化会影响个人的自尊心。
EN: Marginalization can affect an individual's self-esteem.

ZH: 边缘化是一个持续存在的问题。
EN: Marginalization is an ongoing issue.

ZH: 边缘化剥夺了某些人的平等机会。
EN: Marginalization deprives certain people of equal opportunities.

ZH: 边缘化迫使人们生活在贫困之中。
EN: Marginalization forces people to live in poverty.

ZH: 边缘化使得某些群体容易受到歧视。
EN: Marginalization makes certain groups more susceptible to discrimination.

ZH: 边缘化对个人和社会都带来了负面影响。
EN: Marginalization has negative effects on both individuals and society.

ZH: 边缘化加剧了社会的不公平现象。
EN: Marginalization exacerbates social inequalities.

ZH: 这个政策可能会造成更多人的边缘化。
EN: This policy might result in the marginalization of more people.

ZH: 通过教育可以减少边缘化的现象。
EN: Education can help reduce the phenomenon of marginalization.
